Proposed system flow diagram. The input consisted of the actual count taken from the open-source dataset. The data was initially filtered, and the different time series prediction models were applied to the processed data. Six statistical models, viz. Holts forecasting, ETS, AR, MA and ARIMA, SIR, E-SIR, and neural networks forecasting and a data analytics based prediction model was used for predicting the output. The obtained results from each model were compared to find the best-suited model for the prediction

